类 TreePath

  • java.lang.Object
    • source.util.TreePath
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    java.lang.Iterable<Tree>

    @Exported
public class TreePath
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<Tree>
    A path of tree nodes, typically used to represent the sequence of ancestor nodes of a tree node up to the top level CompilationUnitTree node.
    从以下版本开始:
    1.6
    作者:
    Jonathan Gibbons
